'''斜角镜头'''又称'''荷兰式镜头'''（{{lang-en|Dutch angle}}）、'''荷兰式上下直摇'''（{{lang|en|Dutch tilt}}），是一种剧烈移动镜头的拍摄手法，这种镜头手法通常用来表示迷失、迷惑的氛围，令画面失去平衡感。<ref>{{cite web |title=作为一个专业摄影师，这30种镜头你不能不知道！ |url=https://107cine.com/stream/93174/ |website=影视工业网 |accessdate=2020-10-23 |date=2017-07-31 |archive-date=2020-10-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201028030710/https://107cine.com/stream/93174/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=动态视觉基础知识01-镜头角度_俯角|url=http://www.sohu.com/a/337381304_654718|accessdate=2020-10-23|author=|date=|format=|publisher=搜狐|archive-date=2020-10-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201028030709/https://www.sohu.com/a/337381304_654718|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Should You Use A Dutch Angle Shot in Your Films? (Answer: Yes, But...)|url=https://nofilmschool.com/2015/09/should-you-use-dutch-angles-films-yes-but|accessdate=2020-10-25|date=2015-09-04|work=No Film School|language=en|archive-date=2020-10-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201006154554/https://nofilmschool.com/2015/09/should-you-use-dutch-angles-films-yes-but|dead-url=no}}</ref>虽然名为“荷兰式”，这种手法和[[荷兰|荷兰]]并无关系，而是[[德国表现主义|德国表现主义]]电影作品的常用手法<ref>{{Cite web|title=Dutch angle - Hollywood Lexicon|url=http://www.hollywoodlexicon.com/dutchangle.html|accessdate=2020-10-25|work=www.hollywoodlexicon.com|archive-date=2020-02-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200218172850/http://www.hollywoodlexicon.com/dutchangle.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>，因英文{{Linktext|Dutch|lang=en}}和德文{{Linktext|Deutsch|lang=de}}拼写相近而易混淆。具体的做法是在水平方向上倾斜镜头，令其与正常视角的水平线成一角度。<ref>{{Cite web|title=How Subjective Use of the Dutch Angle Camera Technique Evokes Disorienting Doubt Within a Scene|url=https://laughingsquid.com/dutch-angle-camera-technique/|accessdate=2020-10-25|date=2018-04-20|work=Laughing Squid|language=en-US|archive-date=2019-08-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190831003738/https://laughingsquid.com/dutch-angle-camera-technique/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

